dct_description_sm: Verso of 1935 map of Gloucester County, New Jersey. Outside cover features list of the officers and members of Board of Chosen Freeholders, a Historical Sketch of Gloucester County and descriptions of the counties services and characteristics including agriculture, government, local industry, school system and roads and includes six photographs of the area and a drawn illustration of the Red Bank Battle Monument.
